<plot>After their mothers death we find two sisters in the house they grew up in, sitting on the couch they were never allowed on when they were children. Memories pass, good ones and bad ones. The rivalry between the sisters slowly reappears and reaches a climax after the untimely visit of one of the sisters' former lovers.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?638131</url></doc>
